oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Old Dominion Barn Dance - Buck Owens and the Buckaroos - WRVA Part 3
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 3 of an Old Dominion Barn Dance segment featuring Buck Owens and his Buckaroos (performers), on radio station WRVA (Radio Stations : Richmond, Va.) Recording of an unidentified banjo performance also on tape.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Buck Owens and his Buckaroos
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Test tone -- Walking The Floor Over You (Buck Owens and his Buckaroos) [Ernest Tubb impression] -- Walk The Line (Buck Owens and his Buckaroos) [Johnny Cash impression] -- Buck Owens and the band talk and joke with the audience -- Country Music Is Here To Stay (Buck Owens and his Buckaroos) [Ferlin Husky, Simon Crum, Kitty Wells impression] -- Twist And Shout (Buck Owens and his Buckaroos) [Beatles impression] -- Buck and the band talk -- Closing statements -- [Unidentified banjo tune] (incomplete)
